flowchart LR
    User["User Question"] --> UI["React + Vite + Tailwind UI"]
    UI -->|POST /api/query| API["FastAPI API"]
    UI -->|Poll status/result| API
    API --> Repo["SQLite Query Repository"]
    API --> Graph["LangGraph Council Workflow"]
    Graph --> Chair["Chair Agent"]
    Chair --> Scout["Scout Agent"]
    Scout --> Sources["Semantic Scholar + arXiv"]
    Scout --> Chroma["ChromaDB Evidence Store"]
    Chroma --> Reader["Reader Agent"]
    Sources --> Reader
    Reader --> Critic["Critic Agent"]
    Critic --> Synth["Synthesizer Agent"]
    Synth --> Gate{"Confidence >= Threshold?"}
    Gate -->|No| Retry["Visible Retry Event"]
    Retry --> Chair
    Gate -->|Yes| Verdict["Final Verdict Package"]
    Verdict --> Repo
    Repo --> API
    API --> UI

